                        <head>No. 102.<lb/><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Fish</persName> to General <persName type="to">Schenck</persName></hi>.</head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1876-02-17"><hi rend="italic">February</hi> 17,
                                    1876</date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Officer, with papers for Winslow’s extradition, sails Saturday.</p>
                        <closer><signed>FISH,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Secretary</hi>.</signed></closer>
